videos.description: Nursing a one-point lead, Duke's Derryck Thornton makes the game-saving block to give the Blue Devils an improbable win over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Defense wins the game for Duke on final play

videos.description: Duke guard Brandon Ingram talks about how this rivalry game against North Carolina was different than other games throughout the season.
videos.headline: Ingram: 'This was the best game we played this year'

videos.description: Duke guard Grayson Allen discusses No. 20 Duke's big 74-73 road win over in-state rival No. 5 North Carolina.
